title: Super Son-in-law In Another World
description: Super Son-in-law In Another World Manhhua Qin Shi, an ordinary undergraduate, accidentally goes through the time-space journey and becomes the leader of an evil sect. But this sect is so unreliable that the fund is raised by the leader through marital fraud. Qin Shi wants to resign as this position. This story is about a leader who sticks to core socialist values. Outsider Super Son-in-Law Son-in-Law in Another World 异界超级赘婿
